textTemplates.text:
Hi SalesOps,

More than one Contact/Lead was found with the following values:
Email: {!VarEmail}
Bill/Sold To: True

Found Lead IDs: {!Get_Lead}
Found Contact IDs based on email only: {!ContactFirstCollection}
Found Contact IDs based on email and Sold To/Bill To checkbox: {!ContactSecondCollection}
Billing Account ID: {!VarBillingAccountID}

The actions you need to take are:
1. Merge the Contacts/Leads
2. Ensure the new Contacts/Leads is under proper account in Salesforce
3. Update first and last name, address and phone number
